These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, water, 7up
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, skateboarding, badminton
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | mirinda | water | 7up   |
| Sport      | parkour    | skateboarding  | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, 7up
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, russian, indonesian
1. the thai is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the russian is on the far left##1
3. the russian is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | sprite | soy-milk     | 7up      |
| Nationality   | russian | thai | indonesian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite, hot-chocolate
There 3 different types of food: pear, garlic, papaya
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | fanta | hot-chocolate  | sprite       |
| Food       | pear     | garlic | papaya |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: tomato, cauliflower, strawberry
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, sudoku, chess
1. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | strawberry    | cauliflower     | tomato |
| Hobby   | chess | gardening | sudoku     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: goat, cat, mouse
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, skateboard, scooter
1. the person driving the skateboard is the owner of the mouse##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
4. the owner of the goat is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | cat | goat     | mouse |
| Transport   | scooter        | bike | skateboard    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: peas, nectarine, cucumber
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, trike, roller
1. the person eating peas is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person eating cucumber is the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | cucumber | peas      | nectarine  |
| Transport   | van       | trike | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, reggae, metal
3 different pets are kept: frog, dog, hedgehog
1. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
2. the fan of reggae is the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | electronic     | reggae    |
| Pet           | frog | hedgehog | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
