.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, board-games, magic-tricks
3 different pets are kept: fish, bird, turtle
1. the owner of the fish is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | board-games | singing  |
| Pet     | turtle     | fish      | bird |

