.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, water, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, martial-arts, romance
1. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | mirinda   | water    | hot-chocolate    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | fantasy | romance |

