2. the russian is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
3. the egyptian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | country   | gospel  |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | russian | mexican |

