The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, designer, nurse
1. the designer is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
2. the person eating plum is in the middle##1
3. the dancer is on the right of the person eating plum##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food   | grapes     | plum   | spinach     |
| Job    | nurse | designer | dancer |

