.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, almond-milk, mirinda
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, r&b, rock
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
2. the fan of rock is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Beverage      | sprite  | mirinda | almond-milk  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | rock   | folk |

