.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-18::.
There 3 different types of food: radish, eggplant, broccoli
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, tennis, cricket
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person eating radish is the person who's sport is cricket##1
3. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Food    | eggplant | broccoli   | radish        |
| Sport   | tennis    | soccer | cricket |

