.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-19::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing, filmmaking
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, disco, soul
1. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of soul##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the fan of soul##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby         | collecting | rock-climbing | filmmaking |
| Music-Genre   | blues | soul     | disco  |

