.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: watermelon, lemon, cucumber
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, basketball, sailing
1. the person who's sport is basketball is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
3. the person eating lemon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | cucumber | watermelon       | lemon  |
| Sport   | sailing  | basketball | biathlon |

 